Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.00,0:02:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到处都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.26,0:02:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来博士是随身携带了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.97,0:02:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们慢了一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.50,0:02:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士恐怕已经
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.74,0:02:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你逃去哪里\N我们一定会把它弄到手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.05,0:02:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第八十三话\N由太郎归国\N藏在影子下之黑骑士团的野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.76,0:02:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子出去练剑真的很没劲耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.99,0:02:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个道场之前\N还曾经拥有五十个门徒耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么现在落没成那样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.83,0:02:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  以后剑道\N不知道会变成怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.14,0:02:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明治新兴文明开化政策\N把剑道彻底抛弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.17,0:02:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别连剑心你都讲这种丧气话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.58,0:02:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.35,0:02:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算凭我弱女子的一双细手\N我也要把神谷活心流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.95,0:02:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弱女子的细手吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.38,0:03:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好比我的手还粗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.65,0:03:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之我就是壮嘛 哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.03,0:03:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑\N完全不知道别人的辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.26,0:03:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦弥彦不可以说实话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的人是剑心你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了弥彦\N你搬这些进道场吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.07,0:03:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.48,0:03:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 怎么不自己搬嘛\N受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助\N我们不在时有出什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.52,0:03:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.89,0:03:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 这个老头的战法太讨厌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.36,0:03:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有外国来的客人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是谁的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.93,0:03:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外国话！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.20,0:03:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 你说说话呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.11,0:04:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了\N我来自德国我叫做汉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.28,0:04:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.02,0:04:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讲日本话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是左之助 这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.42,0:04:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这招怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.05,0:04:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汉斯老爹不光会日语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.66,0:04:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,棋艺也很精呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经连败五场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.76,0:04:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 将军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.16,0:04:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有认识什么德国人耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.33,0:04:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.83,0:04:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是剑术高手 绯村剑心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我常听到你的事迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.01,0:04:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.14,0:04:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 你名扬德国了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不可能呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.78,0:04:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助 你说明说明呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这招怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是将军 把车吃下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.85,0:04:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.09,0:04:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是\N只有一个门生也是问题哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.90,0:04:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会是来踢馆的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.20,0:05:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明神弥彦就当你对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.44,0:05:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.21,0:05:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥彦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.42,0:05:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.38,0:05:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是老样子呆呆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.85,0:05:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看就知道了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老样子没变的人是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.16,0:05:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的右手呢 伤好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.20,0:05:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别用问的 用这个试试怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我来当你对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那两人很快就打起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.95,0:05:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是跟由太郎同行的人\N左之助你怎么不早说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.92,0:05:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚说什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.15,0:05:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.56,0:05:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还记得吗 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.06,0:05:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩还没分出高低呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.20,0:06:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然记得\N我到德国还继续练剑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.73,0:06:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那正好 看招 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.24,0:06:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这就是真正的剑术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.88,0:06:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.88,0:06:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样跟打架差不多\N喂！你们两个！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.02,0:06:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.22,0:06:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.79,0:06:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那两人很久没碰面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.76,0:06:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.39,0:06:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们口是心非 高兴得很呢\N就让他们打吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.97,0:06:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 弥彦 你认输了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 还早呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.57,0:06:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.01,0:06:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.38,0:06:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汉斯老爹没问题吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太兴奋血压会升高的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也担心着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.71,0:07:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔达斯中尉欢迎光临日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.78,0:07:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是庆祝你们平安抵达的派对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.41,0:07:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就放松下来享受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.02,0:07:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁德尔公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.15,0:07:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有件事我要跟你谈谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请把人遣走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 要讲话随时都行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.03,0:07:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来来 先干一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.83,0:07:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也喝呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.70,0:07:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的酒醒了吧 公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音乐停止演奏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.24,0:07:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位 非常抱歉\N今夜派对到此结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.82,0:08:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我再找机会赔罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.33,0:08:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个以后再忙\N你们快滚 还不快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.57,0:08:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们德意志帝国的精英军官\N找远东小岛的公司想谈什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.41,0:08:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我单刀直入明讲好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.78,0:08:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天起 德意志公司馆\N划入我们的指挥范围了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.72,0:08:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实也没啥大变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.39,0:08:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就假装没看见也不提此事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就当做跟以前一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.00,0:08:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你还想平安回祖国的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.33,0:08:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么资格提这要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.57,0:08:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你被降级到边境来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.24,0:08:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好歹应该还知道这徽章吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.91,0:09:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你们是黑骑士团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.08,0:09:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了慎重起见 我忠告你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.28,0:09:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们发誓忠诚的对象\N不是德意志帝国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.12,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是伟大的指导者 麦斯特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.02,0:09:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑骑士团为什么来日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.43,0:09:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了你的人身安全\N你最好少刺探消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是我要你帮我调查东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.24,0:09:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人应该有来日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.14,0:09:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且还和日本小男孩在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.78,0:09:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你查出他们的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.60,0:09:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汉斯博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.67,0:09:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他应该很累了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.00,0:10:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 在船上\N他也一直在画那奇怪地图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.74,0:10:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为由太郎的右手动手术的\N原来是那位汉斯博士啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.08,0:10:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真看不出来 那个老爹\N竟然是那么高明的大夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.45,0:10:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实他不用去住饭店\N住我们这里就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.42,0:10:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎的伤治好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.39,0:10:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要开个庆祝宴\N庆祝他入门呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.20,0:10:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也对\N我正想找机会答谢汉斯博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.30,0:10:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去红牛怎么样\N明天那里放烟火呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.37,0:10:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先声明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.54,0:10:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不打算庆祝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.11,0:10:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥彦真是 还说负气话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.54,0:10:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是若是要吃牛肉火锅\N就另当别论了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.98,0:10:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也全力赞成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 你就会找理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.69,0:10:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得到地图以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.69,0:10:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直受到不明人士跟踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.94,0:11:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了以防万一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.24,0:11:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必需把这个留下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.88,0:11:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则未来不知会发生什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.68,0:11:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.98,0:11:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.18,0:11:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.19,0:11:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 不知不觉大声吼你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.53,0:11:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要道歉的人是我呀 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.70,0:11:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.63,0:11:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天还要到道场练剑吧\N你早点去睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腰再用力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.82,0:11:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 再挥一百下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.66,0:12:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,双！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.90,0:12:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开壶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二加六是双
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.17,0:12:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.04,0:12:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来再画一笔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.37,0:12:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次 这次我不会输的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 要来几次都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.11,0:12:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开壶！这次是双！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我赌单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.28,0:12:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.72,0:12:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 由太郎 恭喜你的伤好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.56,0:12:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有恭喜你入门神谷活心流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.33,0:12:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是大喜事呀\N今天我们大大庆祝一番吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.00,0:12:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.77,0:12:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是头号弟子\N你是二号别忘记这一点哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.44,0:12:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这没有关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.78,0:12:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这是对前辈的态度吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.91,0:12:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你算什么前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.95,0:12:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.65,0:13:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们俩个别过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.05,0:13:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是由太郎的心情\N比在德国时开朗呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.29,0:13:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.82,0:13:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.29,0:13:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们再打下去\N肉会被左之助全部吃光哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.47,0:13:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助 你太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.07,0:13:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少罗唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.35,0:13:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.32,0:13:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来只好问他本人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.69,0:13:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎的右手伤势很重的\N能够完全治好真了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是西医
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.53,0:13:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汉斯博士\N在德国是出名的医学博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.17,0:13:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且跟德国医学比起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.34,0:13:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本医学不知落后几十年\N不 好几百年呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.71,0:14:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可不能让小惠听到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.95,0:14:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要更努力读书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.48,0:14:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用从博士那里学来的医术\N成为拯救日本人的医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.99,0:14:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对西方人那么崇拜\N亏你还是武士的后代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.96,0:14:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么要打吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.76,0:14:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.37,0:14:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.20,0:14:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拯救病苦的人们\N是不分西方或东方的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.84,0:14:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才研究东方的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.37,0:14:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也因此才跟你熟悉起来的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汉斯博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.68,0:14:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得棋艺跟掷骰子\N都那么精啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.28,0:14:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了\N既然这样我不再手下留情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.19,0:14:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我一定跟你分出胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 比几次都没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.79,0:14:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助还没学乖呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.96,0:14:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么由太郎\N明天也在道场见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.90,0:14:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.00,0:15:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我一定跟你分出胜负\N你可别偷懒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.94,0:15:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.94,0:15:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.94,0:15:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很烦耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.94,0:15:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活该！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.58,0:15:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安\N晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.88,0:15:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 去看完烟火就回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红豆汤不吃了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.72,0:15:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.86,0:15:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎长大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.63,0:15:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还立志成为医生来救许多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.14,0:15:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是某某人\N可以向他看齐就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.57,0:15:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连阿薰都替由太郎讲话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.64,0:15:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎靠医术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.51,0:15:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你靠剑术救人就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.75,0:15:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像剑心那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.95,0:15:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 我才不会输给由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.79,0:15:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩 就是这个志气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.16,0:15:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.96,0:15:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.73,0:16:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神谷道场的人都是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.50,0:16:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了弥彦以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.97,0:16:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来\N弥彦跟你是好朋友哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.14,0:16:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.45,0:16:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.39,0:16:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汉斯博士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.32,0:16:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们为了追你\N大老远跑过来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.49,0:16:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祖国的军人找我有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.53,0:16:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那个东西交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.33,0:16:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个东西？你在讲什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你带在身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.67,0:16:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想死在遥远的异乡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.74,0:16:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 乖乖听话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.05,0:16:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是普通军人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.85,0:16:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是汉斯博士\N很有观察力嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.56,0:17:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难不成…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.99,0:17:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.03,0:17:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎 快点逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.13,0:17:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样 博士 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.43,0:17:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别罗嗦 听我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.29,0:17:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 是地图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情办完了 给他死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.53,0:17:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.90,0:17:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.70,0:17:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也想死吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.98,0:18:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准你们碰这孩子一根汗毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.75,0:18:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太惊人了 没想到\N这偏远地方还会有剑术高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.16,0:18:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是传说中的武士吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.63,0:18:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷兹少尉 这里交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.18,0:18:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.98,0:18:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就当你对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.42,0:18:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修奈特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.49,0:18:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修奈特 撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.01,0:18:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情办完了 走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.28,0:19:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.35,0:19:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎 你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.42,0:19:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士呢 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.42,0:19:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过份 为什么对博士做这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.39,0:19:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汉斯博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.63,0:19:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.96,0:19:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之 赶快带去玄斋大夫那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.77,0:19:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…我跟着却没能保护他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.74,0:19:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.41,0:19:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.88,0:19:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士 我是由太郎 我在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.48,0:19:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我…我把你卷入危险当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.52,0:19:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来日本\N其实是为了寻找某个东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.40,0:19:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某个地方？\N跟被夺走的地图有关吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.50,0:19:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为了以防万一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.57,0:20:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把线索跟地图分开来\N藏在神谷道场的走廊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.41,0:20:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.94,0:20:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守护神圣的灵药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.91,0:20:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能落入他们手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.65,0:20:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士 振作一点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.48,0:20:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大夫 手术准备完毕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.95,0:20:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.39,0:20:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给我跟玄斋大夫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定会救他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.80,0:20:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 拜托你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.80,0:20:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.41,0:20:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算万一日本政府展开行动\N你们也不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.31,0:20:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要得到这个\N剩下的就是迟早的问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.38,0:20:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 这个糟老头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.85,0:20:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不赶快退开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.59,0:20:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没用的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.96,0:21:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有地图\N是找不到你们要找的东西的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.13,0:21:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.03,0:21:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.55,0:21:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奸雄识奸雄\N你们也不用觉得可疑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.98,0:21:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问你是谁呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.49,0:21:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真田忍者头目\N泄矢御沙S
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.46,0:21:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那真是失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.53,0:21:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是信奉骑士道的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.16,0:21:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,容我为刚才\N对淑女的失礼行为道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.83,0:21:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可能\N我想请教先前那段话的下文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.84,0:21:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.85,0:21:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.42,0:22:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是博士的笔记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.16,0:22:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 看来像普通石头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.93,0:22:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎 汉斯博士说的\N神圣的灵药是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.43,0:22:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灵药是指药吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.77,0:22:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.10,0:22:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,线索只有这两个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.41,0:22:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.75,0:22:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽我的微薄之力帮助你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.18,0:22:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 你别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.28,0:22:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
